Frontend (React / JS)
        |
        |  HTTP Request (fetch / REST)
        ↓
Gateway (Express.js API Layer)
        |
        |  Convert JSON → gRPC Object
        |  Serialize using .proto
        ↓
gRPC Client in Gateway
        |
        |  Binary Data over HTTP/2
        ↓
gRPC Server (User / Post / Reaction Service)
        |
        |  Deserialize from Proto
        |  Run business logic
        |  Database (Prisma / PostgreSQL)
        |
        |  Serialize response into Proto
        ↑
gRPC Server → Gateway
        |
        |  Decode Proto → JSON
        ↓
Gateway (Express)
        |
        |  Send JSON response
        ↓
Frontend

Frontend sends HTTP request → Gateway receives it → Gateway converts JSON to gRPC request → Proto serializes the data → gRPC service deserializes → Business logic runs → Result is serialized → Sent back via Proto → Gateway deserializes → Response returned to frontend.
